1.0 - Standard
this will be the standard package (free) of MODX-Boilerplate
- based on prior 1.x
- package management
- no priority support
- standard documentation

______________________


2.0 - Professional
this will be the commercial package of MODX-Boilerplate
- based on prior 1.x
- complete rewrite
- mobile optimized (HTML5Boilerplate like with some improvements)
- Modernizr optimized
- Modernizr 2
- commercial support available (1hr+5 e-mails included)
- pro-documentation with video-tutorials, detailed documentation on ext. component usage (Modernizr, etc.)
- available with themes (1 included per license)

* mobile ADDON
- mobile site framework (HTML5Boilerplate-mobile)


